s='lang-csharp'>public static float MixRestitution(float restitution1, float restitution2)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>restitution1</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.SettingEnv.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The restitution1.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>restitution2</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.SettingEnv.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The restitution2.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
